
'
' Commit Guidelines
' =================
'
' <subject>\n
' <body>\n
' <footer>
'
' Subject:
'   - use the imperative present tense: "change" not "changed",
'   - capitalize first letter, no (.) at the end.
'   - 50 chars max
' Body: like <subject> but 72 chars max
' Footer: place for breaking changes, github issues...
'
' @see interesting resources
'   - https://tbaggery.com/2008/04/19/a-note-about-git-commit-messages.html
'   - https://dhwthompson.com/2019/my-favourite-git-commit
